# Gradle wrapper jar — INTENTIONALLY NOT IGNORED.
# Once `gradle wrapper` has been run once (locally or in CI), commit the
# resulting android/gradle/wrapper/gradle-wrapper.jar so future clean
# checkouts don't depend on the bootstrap step. The CI workflow regenerates
# it on-demand if absent.
# (no entry needed — listed here only as documentation)

